::: {.cell-output-display}
![Average difference in Wisconsin residential and Mont Belvieu propane prices (per gallon) separated by increase from Mont Belvieu to Wisconsin wholesale price (blue) and from Wisconsin wholesale to residential price (red) for EIA-defined heating seasons (October to March) since 2013-14.](index_files/figure-html/fig-WIbreakdown-1.png){#fig-WIbreakdown fig-align='center' width=672}
:::
